        <item>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Border Bonds for America Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of the Treasury to issue up to $5 billion in bonds in a fiscal year, with proceeds going into a trust fund for the construction of reinforced fencing, physical barriers and related infrastructure for the U.S. southwest border with Mexico.<br> </p>]]></text>
